step.context:
\text{If }I=\int \dfrac{\cos x}{\sqrt{1 + \sin x}}\,dx 
= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}} \, dt   \\
\text{then does this look correct?}

step.tex:
\begin{align}
  I &= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}}\, dt
      = 2 \sqrt t + C \\
    &= 2\sqrt{1 + \sin x} + C    
\end{align}

\begin{align}
  I &= \int \dfrac{1}{\sqrt{t}} \, dt
      = \dfrac{1}{2} \sqrt t + C \\
    &= \dfrac{1}{2} \sqrt{1 + \sin x} + C    
\end{align}
